@node menu "The Game"

  'Game_of_Knights' is a 2-player Workbench game based on the Knights movement
on a Chess board. the idea is simple: each player try to move on more tiles than
his (or her) opponent.

  When a player leaves a tile, that tile is marked with the player's colour and
cannot be used again by either players.

  An important strategy is to try to 'trap' the opposing player so that he (or
she) cannot move.

  Have fun!

